snippet.textDisplay: Ok so I’m sacred like hella scared of clowns before... like I’m still scared but not as much as I was couple years back. I wouldn’t mind going to a circus as long as I’m not too close of contact to the clowns.... But I had a dream on a Thursday night that the next morning during trail day at school my group who’s on the purple trail will be meet with a clown holding a chain saw on the other side of the little hill we had to cross in order to finish of where we wanted our trail to end.....So I was freaking out and told everyone to back up and start running back to the entrance and call for help... but I wasn’t take it my eyes off the clown...If anything I was actually ready to square up... the clown was coming closer and I started backing away and picked up a really big stick just in case (didn’t know how it was going to be a match for a chainsaw but hey at least I got something.) It started running and I started running entering the field and I saw my principal and classmates just up the the play ground and told them to run. The clown was still chasing me as I looked behind me and I entered the school building and told the teachers to lock all of the doors everyone was scrambling locking any enter way Into the building...Then my dream stop there I woke up the next morning almost forgetting it was trail day and I was so anxious for the time of trail... I didn’t say anything bc I didn’t want to freak anyone out on the trail today especially the little kids... so when it was time to enter the trail I immediately picked up the same stick in my dream but the only thing missing was the clown... I thought it moved to a different location in the trail but I never encountered a clown... thankfully it’s my last year at school so I’m safe.... or at least I think I am.....
